lead_paragraph: South Florida's Quinton Flowers says there were a lot of big-name college football programs that thought he could be a star player. As a running back. Or maybe as a safety.

headline.print_headline: No. 25 S Florida Beats S Carolina 46-39 in Birmingham Bowl
